column1: # The February 1941 reading is an estimate and has been omitted.
# The June 1941 reading is an estimate and has been omitted.
# For 1944, the readings for every month except January and August are estimates and have been omitted.
# The readings for February and March 1947 are estimated for snow and have been retained.
# Readings for August, November and December 1951 are estimates and have been omitted.
# The station continued until 1976 according to MIDAS.
